 cycle progression highlighted in this\nstudy provide useful constraints to discern among the multitude of solar dynamo\nmodels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2016 17:49:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-07"}
