ized gluon distribution should exist due to\n$Q^2$ evolution, even if it were zero at a low $Q^2$ scale. The\ntensor-polarized gluon distribution has never been observed, so that it is an\ninteresting future project.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2016 00:45:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2016 12:14:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-28"}
