c{1-2q}{1-q} \\theta (0 \\leq\nq \\leq \\frac{1}{2})$, which has been found previously in various other\nLocalization problems in spaces of effective infinite dimensionality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2016 09:21:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2016 12:07:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-16"}
